window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>After getting her heartbroken by a past lover, Aurora promised to never give it away again.</p> <p>Years later she's focused on growing her brand, love wasn't on the agenda. When a blast from the past comes and shakes her world up she's left trying to ignore the feelings she buried long ago.</p> <p>Not only is there a battle between her heart and mind, but she's dealing with a terminal illness in her family too.</p> <p>Join the middle Parker sister and learn if she finally learns to let grudges go and accept her second chance at love.</p> <p>Contains mature themes.</p>"; 
